  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Season snapper fillets with salt and pepper.",
    "Grill snapper for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Heat vegetable oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add sliced eggplant and cook until tender, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add sliced onion and minced garlic and cook until softened, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add diced tomato and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add cooked snapper to the wok or skillet and stir in patis and sambal oelek.",
    "Serve snapper with Filipino stir-fry and cooked rice.",
